metadata.name: 『Friendship bond』
metadata.description:
“There is no better feeling than spending time with your best friend. The opportunity to share your sincere laughter with a friend is a great happiness. Appreciate the people you call friends and the time you spend with them, because everything has an 𝗲𝗻𝗱.”
